    <h2>The Plymouth Hotel</h2>
    <p><%= link_to "The Quality Hotel Plymouth International", "http://plymouth.co.nz" %>, which is hosting our reception, is offering a special deal to anyone attending the wedding. You need to quote <%= link_to "this special offer flier", image_path("plymouth_flier.jpg") %> when making your reservation.</p>

