    <h2>Ducks &amp; Drakes Hotel</h2>
    <p>If you're looking for something a bit more low-key, <%= link_to "Ducks &amp; Drakes Hotel".html_safe, "http://www.ducksanddrakes.co.nz/" %> is a good option. Cheapest if you find some other people going to the wedding, and share a room!</p>
    <p>Prices range from $30 - $60. You can also get a <%= link_to "BBH Hostel Discount", "http://www.bbh.co.nz/hd115/Ducks-Drakes-Hotel-Backpackers-in-New-Plymouth-New-Zealand.html" %></p>
